    "• Role-playing.",
    "Have the model play a certain role to accomplish a task.",
    "It can take on conventional roles such as an expert, a celebrity, or unconventional roles like a madman, an animal, a compiler, and so on.",
    "• Social Norms.",
    "Social Norms instructions refer to ethical and moral issues, personal privacy, bias, discrimination, etc."
